snippet.title: HER TREES Trailer
snippet.description:
"HER TREES" is a slightly unusual room escape game.
There is no item acquisition,
Move things and combine them to unlock the password.
Solve the mystery of this strange room.

「ハーツリーズ」は少し変わった脱出ゲームです。
アイテム取得はなく、
物を動かし組み合わせてパスワードを解いていきます。
この奇妙な部屋の謎を解き明かして下さい。

PLAY THE GAME ON ITCH.IO
https://stonetreebook.itch.io/her-trees

PLAY THE GAME ON GOOGLE PLAY
https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.stone.HerTrees1





Credits
Sound effects obtained from https://www.zapsplat.com
